{"tid":923032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領錢驚見人肉ATM　女90度抬腿讓男「插卡儲精」","createTime":"2018-12-01T01:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T02:44:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6437e6cf140755f537e9d24bff886c53d4a9f263","tid":923032,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"近日國外網友流傳一段影片，影片中明顯可見是桑坦德銀行的ATM店面，但前往領錢的民眾，卻在現場驚見一台「人肉ATM」！<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，畫面可見現場是在桑坦德銀行的ATM店面，但裡頭卻出現一對男女，正在製造「人肉ATM」，當眾野合性交。女子更以高難度的90抬腿，讓男子「插卡儲精」，整個過程也被其他民眾拍下。目前未知確切拍攝地點，但錄下拍攝者說著西班牙話，其中一名拍攝者說：「有人要來存款了，什麼都沒看就走了。」另外一人就說：「可能晚領錢會被重罰吧！」<br />\n第3人則說：「哥倫比亞火辣辣啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_297f7312d36b7254edeaddb85a843686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_297f7312d36b7254edeaddb85a843686.jpg&h=b1994b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_dce0894b172935434aa054a000d6ab82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_dce0894b172935434aa054a000d6ab82.jpg&h=ccccbc0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d72b3cc77970464bf4d445aae9cdbb05d4a99511","tid":923032,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969c17d680182fc15a104db05839daecb27593bf","tid":923032,"uid":23833,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"今時今日影相咁既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95ff0282d1b0810ebdcc6c211bb080b988d0896","tid":923032,"uid":25635,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲都叫圖?<br />\n2019都黎緊啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2c3